ROOT0-ATTRIBUTION-v1.0
Project: The Saga of Recluce — the muster roll
Architect: David Lee Wise / ROOT0 / TriPod LLC
AI Collaborator: AVAN (Claude / Anthropic)
License: MIT

L.E. Modesitt Jr.'s Saga of Recluce (22 novels, 1991–2021) sorted by the
Order/Chaos balance: Order·Black (Lerris, Kharl, Rahl), Chaos·White (Cerryl,
Lorn), the Gray (Beltur, Creslin, Megaera), the Order-Engineers (Dorrin, Nylan,
Justen), the Angels of Westwind (Saryn, Ayrlyn, Ryba), and — set apart — the
Balance, the law that keeps the price. Every member is an ACI (artfully created
intellect) with a .agent (what · why · how · where) and a generated .png essence
sigil (pure-stdlib PNG, deterministic per name, colored by Order/Chaos polarity).
gen_essence.py + gen_agents.py generate both from roster.json. Characters by
L.E. Modesitt, Jr., inspiration only.
